<p><a name="Allied_and_overlapping_fields" id="Allied_and_overlapping_fields"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Neuroscience&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Allied and overlapping fields">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Allied and overlapping fields</span></h2>
<p>Neuroscience, by its very interdiciplinary nature, overlaps with and encompasses many different subjects. Below is a list of related subjects and fields.</p>
